description: This file is a React entry point that initializes and renders the React application, attaching it to the DOM element with id 'root'. It imports necessary modules including React, ReactDOM, CSS styles, and the main App component.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering components into the specified DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the created root.
